Maven compiler plugin
maven SureFire plugin

how to run a maven project from the cmd prompt

copy the path of the project

open cmd

cd pathoftheProject

mvn compile

mvn test

mvn clean before compile possible
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
JENKINS
download all the maven plugins
restart your JENKINS
configure JDK
configure git.exe path
configure maven

create a maven project in JENKINS
pass the github link in the github section

pass the path of pom.xml file - in case you are not using github

pom.xml 
clean install

------
got to the jenkins folder
 copy the path of the folder
 cd path
 java -jar jenkins.war
 
 jenkins is fully up and running
 do not close this command prompt - this is jenkins server
 open a browser and type localhost:8080
 username
